         <abstract id="aspace_e741d939cd5ba6cf6064c49ef5d2a25a">Collection of black and white glass lantern slides of cave paintings from Dunhuang (Gansu province, China) and works from other sites including Khotan, Kucha, and Turfan.</abstract>
      </did>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_arest">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_urest">
