      <prefercite id="aspace_cite">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Dunhuang (China) and Central Asian Lantern Slide Collection</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection of black and white glass lantern slides of cave paintings from Dunhuang (Gansu province, China) and works from other sites including Khotan, Kucha, and Turfan.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged alphabetically by medium. Dunhuang paintings sub-divided by cave number. Central Asian material sub-arranged by site.</p>  
      </arrangement>
